Feature: hello command

  Scenario: hello outputs a greeting
    When I run the CLI with "hello"
    Then the command succeeds
    And the output contains "Hello"

  Scenario: hello accepts a custom name
    When I run the CLI with "hello --name World"
    Then the command succeeds
    And the output contains "Hello, World"

  Scenario: CLI help shows project summary
    When I run the CLI with "--help"
    Then the command succeeds
    And the output contains "{{ project_summary }}"
